---

<Layout>
  <main style="padding: 48px 24px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: system-ui;">
    <h1>TriAxis Resources</h1>
    <p style="max-width: 70ch; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6;">
      We are a South African commodities trading business focused on reliable supply, transparent processes, and long-term partnerships.
    </p>

    <div style="display: grid; gap: 16px; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); margin-top: 28px;">
      <div style="border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px;">
        <h3>Commodities</h3>
        <p>Coal and related commodities.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px;">
        <h3>Logistics</h3>
        <p>Reliable loading and dispatch coordination.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px;">
        <h3>Contact</h3>
        <p>Email: info@triaxis.net.za</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
